                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12449480" author="brj" created="Mon, 13 Nov 2006 20:16:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the variable  searchStringEscape must be correctly set in org.apache.openjpa.jdbc.sql.MySQLDictionary:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...&lt;br/&gt;
 searchStringEscape = &quot;\\\\&quot;;&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12449481" author="mprudhom" created="Mon, 13 Nov 2006 20:22:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note that you should be able to work around the issue for the time being by setting the property &quot;openjpa.jdbc.DBDictionary&quot; to &quot;searchStringEscape=&lt;br class=&quot;atl-forced-newline&quot; /&gt;&quot; in your persistence.xml file or in the properties you use to create the EntityManagerFactory.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
